```
Done. This .gitignore:
1. **Commits ALL RAG data** (rag_db/ folder and all embeddings completely)
2. **No exclusions** for code_chunks.lance - pre-built embeddings are stored
3. **Instant context** - other devs download embeddings with the repo
4. **No rebuild** needed - works even on machines without LLM/embedding capability

